  "A rocket engine burns liquid hydrogen with liquid oxygen: 2H2(l) + O2(l) -> 2H2O(g), Delta H = -484 kJ. If the rocket needs 10,000 kJ of energy, how many grams of H2 are required? (MW H2 = 2.0 g/mol)": "",
